  abstract={It is shown that the power set of $κ$ ordered by the subset relation modulo various versions of the non-stationary deal can be embedded into the partial order of Borel equivalence relations on $2^κ$ under Borel reducibility. Here $κ$ is uncountable regular cardinal with $κ^{<κ} = κ$.},
